PEPMOB websites

to get apache webserver, download xanpp package, has mqsql and php all installed

xanpp gets installed into root dir

go to htdocs, that's where you put JS and PHP files

go to xanpp control panel, get option to start services

skype binds to port 80, have to change default port for apache from 80, go to apache config httpd.conf, set 'listen'

go to localhost:81/ in browser, apache will serve up whatever's in htdocs folder
- can reset this folder in httpd.conf under DocumentRoot

